OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777558269
OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee over
OL,4,C'lack of focus' on saving money
OL,6,FA Guernsey politician has resigned
OL,7,Ffrom the Employment and Social
OL,8,FSecurity Committee (ESS) after
OL,9,Fbecoming "increasingly frustrated by
OL,10,Fthe lack of focus to identify and
OL,11,Fdeliver meaningful savings".
OL,13,FDeputy David Dorrity adds that he made
OL,14,Fthe decision "with some regret" and
OL,15,Facknowledges "the difficult job of
OL,16,Fbalancing public finances with
OL,17,Fproviding for the genuine needs of the
OL,18,Fpeople of Guernsey".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
