FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777558269
OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee over
OL,4,C'lack of focus' on saving money
OL,6,FHowever, after raising concerns and
OL,7,Ftrying to work with members to lower
OL,8,Fspending, he concludes: "I have come
OL,9,Fto feel that members of the ESS
OL,10,FSavings Working Group have been
OL,11,Ffighting an uphill battle, with a lack
OL,12,Fof willingness to make the difficult
OL,13,Fdecisions which I believe are
OL,14,Fnecessary."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777558269
OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee over
OL,4,C'lack of focus' on saving money
OL,6,FThe Committee's President, Deputy Tina
OL,7,FBury, says she is "disappointed and a
OL,8,Flittle surprised" at the decision, but
OL,9,Fadds: "He has made a valuable
OL,10,Fcontribution so far this term,
OL,11,Fespecially with his expertise in
OL,12,Fpensions, which I'd like to thank him
OL,13,Ffor."
OL,15,FShe continues: "The work of ESS, which
OL,16,Finvolves balancing support for the
OL,17,Flowest earners and most vulnerable in
OL,18,Four community and being financially
OL,19,Fresponsible overall, is no mean feat
OL,20,Fand, at times, very challenging.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
