OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777558269
OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee over
OL,4,C'lack of focus' on saving money
OL,6,F"The ESS savings working group has
OL,7,Falready identified around 30 actions
OL,8,Fthat could be pursued. This work must
OL,9,Fbe thorough though.
OL,11,F"We must understand the savings that
OL,12,Fcould potentially be made, but also
OL,13,Fcarefully consider the consequences of
OL,14,Fany changes, and that will take some
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
